# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages an HAProxy map file on OPNsense. Map files store key/value routing tables such as domain-to-backend mappings for `map_use_backend` actions. Requires the `os-haproxy` plugin.

OPNsense stores mapfile content as one object. This provider normalizes trailing whitespace in `content` to avoid drift from heredoc trailing newlines. Keep one mapping per line, with values matching the HAProxy backend names that HAProxy resolves at runtime.

